Package: SSI
Type: Package
Title: The package provides functions to compute the Systematicty of Search Index (SSI)
Version: 0.1.0
Imports: data.table, plyr, dplyr
Author: Sonja Perkovic
Maintainer: Sonja Perkovic <bnsp@leeds.ac.uk>
Description: The package provides functions to compute the Systematicity of Search Index (SSI) by identifying alternative-wise and attribute-wise patterns in a sequence of eye fixations. The SSI measures the proportion of systematic or non-random search and it is a useful measure for exploring information search behavior.
License: GPL-3 + MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
